reviewText: The Discovery Channel does it again. This video has some of the most incredible footage of all aspects of hurricanes, from 200 hundred miles up in space, or right inside of the beast. This video shows hurricanes,  typhoons, and cyclones from decades past to recent years. Most incrledible  is the slow motion photography of hurricane destruction. You will  defininetley have a new respect for the power of nature after watching this  video.
